[SN]TITLE[SN]
Pelsall robber struggles to escape Co-op raid with heavy coins haul

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An armed robber who stashed a huge haul of coins in a holdall was spotted "struggling and staggering" as he tried to escape with the weighty load.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The man threatened staff with a handgun at the Co-op store in Pelsall, West Midlands, at 06.20 BST.
He stole a large quantity of coins before struggling with the weight of the haul as he fled, West Midlands Police said.
Police declined to say how much cash was taken in the raid.
